OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright start under some high
OL,6,Fcloud, sunny spells turning hazy. More
OL,7,Fin the way of sunshine by the middle
OL,8,Fpart of the afternoon. Staying very
OL,9,Fwarm for many in light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA mostly dry night to come
OL,12,Fwith high cloud around. A few isolated
OL,13,Fshowers possible, but a much more
OL,14,Fcomfortable night for many compare to
OL,15,Frecent nights.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FLow cloud to start with, but
OL,18,Flifting through the morning and into
OL,19,Fthe afternoon. Isolated showers
OL,20,Fdeveloping, with sunny spells in
OL,21,Fbetween. Warm, but cooler than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
